title: [Dye Mad About It, Backroom]
description: One exceptionally large purple paper lantern hangs from the peak of the wagon's ceiling, with slashed vents in the orb allowing spears of light to streak across the area.  On the back wall is a glass case filled with rows and rows of glass eyes, all manner of colors accounted for, and beneath it is a table laden with bottles, bags, and beakers full of ingredients, reagents, and other indiscernible contents.
